## Prisma
# Postgres example:
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:5432/DB_NAME?schema=public"
#
# TLS notes:
# - If your Postgres requires TLS, set:
#   DATABASE_SSL=true
# - If you get "unable to verify the first certificate" (common with self-signed / missing CA chain),
#   you can disable verification (NOT recommended for production):
#   DATABASE_SSL_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=false


